wifi-qr (0.4-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Automatically detect GUI dialog tool (Zenity or KDialog).
    - Add manual dialog tool selection with -d option.
  * Improve keyboard navigation support (Bug #27).
  * Add webcam-based QR scanning functionality (Bug #25).
  * Enhance QR data parsing.
    - Add legacy encoding support (Bug #23).
    - Improve parsing of WIFI URI (Bug #22).
  * Remove deprecated Zenity code.
  * Apply ShellCheck recommendations to improve script quality.
  * Add AppStream metadata for better software center integration.
  * Update copyright year to 2024.
  * Extend source ignore patterns to include README and Screenshots.

 -- kokoye2007 <kokoye2007@gmail.com>  Wed, 18 Dec 2024 02:28:22 +1100

